{"word":"H425 - אֵלָה - ʼÊlâh - ay-law' - Elah","slug":"H425","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">אֵלָה</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ʼÊlâh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ay-law'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Elah"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Original: <b><he>אלה</he></b> <p />Transliteration: <b>'êlâh</b> <p />Phonetic: <b>ay-law'</b> <p class=\"bdb_def\"><b>BDB Definition</b>:</p> Elah = \"An oak\" <ol><li>an Edomite chief</li><li>a king of Israel for two years, son of Baasha</li><li>the father of king Hoshea of Israel</li><li>a son of Caleb</li><li>son of Uzzi</li></ol> <p />Origin: the same as <a href=\"#/H424\">H424</a> <p />TWOT entry: None <p />Part(s) of speech: Proper Name "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H193\">H193</a>, <a href=\"#/H195\">H195</a>, <a href=\"#/H197\">H197</a>, <a href=\"#/H198\">H198</a>, <a href=\"#/H352\">H352</a>, <a href=\"#/H354\">H354</a>, <a href=\"#/H355\">H355</a>, <a href=\"#/H356\">H356</a>, <a href=\"#/H357\">H357</a>, <a href=\"#/H359\">H359</a>, <a href=\"#/H361\">H361</a>, <a href=\"#/H362\">H362</a>, <a href=\"#/H364\">H364</a>, <a href=\"#/H365\">H365</a>, <a href=\"#/H424\">H424</a>, <a href=\"#/H436\">H436</a>, <a href=\"#/H440\">H440</a>"}]}